<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Plastic Pay | Recycle & Earn</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Plastic Pay</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Recycle Plastic. Earn Points. Redeem Rewards.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="about">
        <h2>About the Project</h2>
        <p>
            Plastic Pay is an initiative designed to reduce plastic waste by encouraging
            people to pick up and deposit plastic in a Reverse Vending Machine (RVM).  
            Each deposit earns points on the Plastic Pay mobile app, and these points can be
            redeemed for amazing gifts and rewards.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step">
                <h3>1. Collect Plastic</h3>
                <p>Pick up used plastic bottles, cans, or containers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <h3>2. Deposit in RVM</h3>
                <p>Drop them into our Reverse Vending Machine near you.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <h3>3. Earn Points</h3>
                <p>Each deposit gives you points on the Plastic Pay app.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <h3>4. Redeem Gifts</h3>
                <p>Exchange your points for exciting gifts and rewards.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="goal">
        <h2>Our Goal</h2>
        <p>* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

body {
    background: #f5f9ff;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    background: #2a82ff;
    color: white;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.tagline {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}

section {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
}

h2 {
    color: #2a82ff;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.about p, .goal p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #444;
}

.steps-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.step {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
}

.step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #2a82ff;
    color: white;
    margin-top: 30px;
}
            To support the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs), especially
            **Responsible Consumption & Production (SDG 12)** and **Climate Action (SDG 13)** by
            reducing plastic pollution and promoting recycling.
        </p>
    </section>

